      • asVolatileComponent

        public T asVolatileComponent​(boolean isVolatileComponent)
        Mark the component that will be registered in the registration phase as virtual. ION Daemon will not keep track of any details of the new component.
        This feature is useful when the component name is randomly generated.

        Note: this flag is not forwarded to ION Daemon when set to false for backward compatibility.
        Check ION Daemon compatibility before setting this flag to true.

        Parameters:
        isVolatileComponent - true to mark the component as volatile, false otherwise.
        Returns:
        this builder.
